INSERT INTO elements VALUES('id364e333f',2,'idba79d8ef','General Taldarax','{"description": "A battle-hardened military leader with a deep sense of honor and commitment to protecting the galaxy from external threats. General Taldarax''s strategic prowess and unwavering resolve make him a formidable force in intergalactic conflicts.", "details": "General Taldarax is known for his exceptional tactical skills, having honed them through years of experience in leading complex military operations in different galaxies. He carries a sense of burden for the lives under his command and strives to minimize casualties during conflicts. Taldarax is also a firm believer in diplomacy, often seeking peaceful resolutions before engaging in warfare. Despite his imposing stature, he is known for his fairness and empathy, earning the respect of both his allies and adversaries.", "personality": "General Taldarax is disciplined, principled, and resolute. He exudes an aura of authority and commands respect through his actions rather than just his rank. Despite his stoic demeanor, he deeply cares about the well-being of his subordinates and seeks to inspire courage and loyalty in those under his command. Taldarax values integrity, honor, and the preservation of life above all, striving to uphold these principles in the face of adversity."}',0);
INSERT INTO elements VALUES('idf5229599',1,'','Trumpland: The Dystopian Legacy','{"description": "Trumpland is a dystopian world ruled by an authoritarian regime, characterized by propaganda, social inequality, environmental degradation, and the oppressive grip of power. The legacy of Donald Trump looms large, shaping the world''s identity and its struggles.", "details": "In Trumpland, society is deeply divided, with the ruling elite living in luxury while the rest of the population struggles to survive in poverty and squalor. The environment has suffered catastrophic damage due to the policies of the authoritarian regime, leading to widespread pollution and ecological disaster. The people are subjected to constant propaganda and surveillance, and dissent is brutally suppressed. The heavy-handed tactics of the Trumpian regime have left their mark on the landscape, transforming once vibrant cities into bleak, decaying urban centers, and imposing iconic structures and statues in honor of the ruling figures.", "plans": "Items:\n1. The Legacy Key: A symbolic artifact that unlocks the truth about the regime''s dark secrets.\n2. The Oppression Mask: An enigmatic mask that grants its wearer the power to blend in and evade surveillance.\n3. Propaganda Poster\n4. Resistance Symbol\n5. Corruption Data File"}',0);
