INSERT INTO images VALUES('id763ad166','idf5229599','Trumpland: The Dystopian Legacy is a dystopian world ruled by an authoritarian regime, characterized by propaganda, social inequality, environmental degradation, and the oppressive grip of power. The legacy of Donald Trump looms large, shaping the world''s identity and its struggles. In Trumpland, society is deeply divided, with the ruling elite living in luxury while the rest of the population struggles to survive in poverty and squalor. The environment has suffered catastrophic damage due to the policies of the authoritarian regime, leading to widespread pollution and ecological disaster. The people are subjected to constant propaganda and surveillance, and dissent is brutally suppressed. The heavy-handed tactics of the Trumpian regime have left their mark on the landscape, transforming once vibrant cities into bleak, decaying urban centers, and imposing iconic structures and statues in honor of the ruling figures.','6aa17fd47a69f38d9fb12242.png',0);
