INSERT INTO images VALUES('id16b6f192','idcda75ecb','An image of Smog City, once a bustling metropolis, now a grim testament to the environmental degradation and industrial pollution that plagues Trumpland. The skies are perpetually shrouded in toxic smog, casting a sickly pallor over the city. Dilapidated buildings and rusting infrastructure dominate the landscape, and the air is heavy with the acrid stench of pollution. Despite its decay, Smog City remains a place of underground resistance and hidden hope for change, with pockets of resilient inhabitants fighting to reclaim the city from its toxic oppressors.','5615b93f6235c633b8378669.png',0);
INSERT INTO images VALUES('ide0335934','id4fc9badf','An image of The Resistance Headquarters, a hidden stronghold, a clandestine hub of organization and rebellion against the oppressive rule of TrumpWorld. Tucked away from prying eyes and surveillance, this covert base serves as a center for coordinating resistance efforts, sharing vital information, and planning daring acts of defiance. Accessible only to trusted allies, the headquarters harbors the hopes and aspirations of those who refuse to surrender to the tyranny of the regime. Within its walls, a flame of rebellion burns bright, fueling the fight for freedom in the face of overwhelming adversity.','2054683b095a6387cf5fb177.png',0);
INSERT INTO images VALUES('id32687c89','id2f78da60','An image of Dr. Amelia Frost, a brilliant and beautiful scientist from Northern California, dedicated to finding solutions to environmental crises in the midst of Trumpland''s chaos. With piercing eyes that reflect her passion, she stands tall against the backdrop of nature, embodying both resilience and hope as she works tirelessly to protect the environment and innovate sustainable solutions in the face of tyranny.','9bc11a69035c721340e0b256.png',0);
INSERT INTO images VALUES('iddd8aaf2b','id2356e59c','An image of Stark, the seasoned wanderer with a mysterious past, traversing the diverse landscapes of Wanderer World. He is known for his exceptional tracking skills and survival instincts, and his eyes reflect a sense of reserved determination.','0d3288b99909b0766bf2346c.png',0);
